00:12:52.272 --> 00:12:54.007 align:middle line:84%
They are connected
with other people.

00:12:54.007 --> 00:12:56.443 align:middle line:84%
They are connected
with the planet.

00:12:56.443 --> 00:12:59.646 align:middle line:84%
And this last aspect,
they hardly ever talk

00:12:59.646 --> 00:13:02.816 align:middle line:84%
about it spontaneously, you
