00:13:02.816 --> 00:13:06.586 align:middle line:84%
Because they are so overwhelmed
by it and so frightened by it

00:13:06.586 --> 00:13:10.557 align:middle line:84%
because you just feel
what other people think

00:13:10.557 --> 00:13:13.994 align:middle line:84%
or what other people feel or
you know he have a premonition

00:13:13.994 --> 00:13:15.795 align:middle line:90%
that someone will die.

00:13:15.795 --> 00:13:18.465 align:middle line:90%
And after few weeks, people--

00:13:18.465 --> 00:13:22.802 align:middle line:84%
this man really dies and
