00:13:22.802 --> 00:13:25.538 align:middle line:84%
So they have this enhanced
intuitive sensitivity,

00:13:25.538 --> 00:13:28.842 align:middle line:84%
it's because they are
connected with aspect

00:13:28.842 --> 00:13:30.343 align:middle line:90%
of consciousness of others.

00:13:30.343 --> 00:13:33.313 align:middle line:84%
>> So how do you define
now this consciousness then

00:13:33.313 --> 00:13:35.548 align:middle line:84%
if it's not created
by the brain,

00:13:35.548 --> 00:13:38.318 align:middle line:84%
if it's separated,
if it's non-local.

00:13:38.318 --> 00:13:39.819 align:middle line:90%
What is it?

00:13:39.819 --> 00:13:43.690 align:middle line:84%
>> Yeah. At first, I don't
have a real good definition

00:13:43.690 --> 00:13:47.694 align:middle line:84%
of consciousness because in so
many aspects of consciousness

00:13:47.694 --> 00:13:52.898 align:middle line:84%
but the main finding for--
and conclusion for us all is

00:13:52.898 --> 00:13:56.269 align:middle line:84%
that we have to discuss again
the never proven assumption

00:13:56.269 --> 00:13:59.205 align:middle line:84%
that consciousness is
product of brain function,

00:13:59.205 --> 00:14:01.741 align:middle line:84%
because when the brain
doesn't function at all,

00:14:01.741 --> 00:14:04.210 align:middle line:84%
people have this
enhanced consciousness.

00:14:04.210 --> 00:14:08.181 align:middle line:84%
And in this, it has
consciousness, they have access

00:14:08.181 --> 00:14:14.187 align:middle line:84%
to the past where they are
connected also with thoughts

00:14:14.187 --> 00:14:16.189 align:middle line:84%
of other people in
the past as well.

00:14:16.189 --> 00:14:21.761 align:middle line:84%
They feel [inaudible] they
relive their whole life mostly

00:14:21.761 --> 00:14:25.432 align:middle line:84%
where they are with
a being of light--

00:14:25.432 --> 00:14:28.335 align:middle line:84%
of with the light which
is unconditional love

00:14:28.335 --> 00:14:33.106 align:middle line:84%
and also access to
knowledge, to wisdom,

00:14:33.106 --> 00:14:36.576 align:middle line:84%
do get all the answers
before you ask the questions.

00:14:36.576 --> 00:14:41.548 align:middle line:84%
It's-- they also can
have a flash forward

00:14:41.548 --> 00:14:43.383 align:middle line:90%
to see future events.

00:14:43.383 --> 00:14:47.454 align:middle line:84%
So they are in a realm,
in a dimension where time

00:14:47.454 --> 00:14:50.290 align:middle line:84%
and space doesn't
play a role anymore.

00:14:50.290 --> 00:14:53.093 align:middle line:84%
Everything is at the
same moment there.

00:14:53.093 --> 00:14:56.663 align:middle line:84%
So they have a cardiac
arrest of two minutes.

00:14:56.663 --> 00:14:59.232 align:middle line:84%
You can talk for hours to
days about what happened

00:14:59.232 --> 00:15:02.836 align:middle line:84%
because everything
happened at the same time.

00:15:02.836 --> 00:15:05.438 align:middle line:84%
This is what you call
interconnectedness

00:15:05.438 --> 00:15:08.375 align:middle line:84%
and you can call it non-locality
because there is no time,

00:15:08.375 --> 00:15:12.379 align:middle line:84%
no space, everything
happens at the same moment.

00:15:12.379 --> 00:15:16.282 align:middle line:90%
And so for me, the conclusion is

00:15:16.282 --> 00:15:20.120 align:middle line:84%
that the brain doesn't
produce consciousness

00:15:20.120 --> 00:15:23.323 align:middle line:84%
but the brain has a
facilitating function.

00:15:23.323 --> 00:15:26.426 align:middle line:84%
It makes it possible to
experience consciousness.

00:15:26.426 --> 00:15:28.395 align:middle line:84%
>> I like your analogy
