an end to consciousness?

00:22:41.661 --> 00:22:43.162 align:middle line:90%
And I think no.

00:22:43.162 --> 00:22:45.898 align:middle line:84%
There's no beginning, no
end to-- it's infinite.

00:22:45.898 --> 00:22:49.135 align:middle line:84%
It's endless because
there's no beginning, no end.

00:22:49.135 --> 00:22:52.138 align:middle line:84%
Everything past or
future is available.

00:22:52.138 --> 00:22:53.673 align:middle line:90%
Everything is there.

00:22:53.673 --> 00:22:57.176 align:middle line:84%
So non-local consciousness
is always ever inside

00:22:57.176 --> 00:23:01.514 align:middle line:84%
