You can have non-local
healing or distance.

00:23:21.067 --> 00:23:24.237 align:middle line:84%
So you can have this
non-local perturbation

00:23:24.237 --> 00:23:27.240 align:middle line:84%
which means matters change
because of consciousness

00:23:27.240 --> 00:23:30.042 align:middle line:84%
